related_questions.question: Is a backpack a good carry on?
related_questions.snippet: Most airlines allow you to bring on one personal item such as a purse or briefcase, as well as one larger item such as a backpack. For many airlines, the maximum size of a carry-on item is 22 by 14 by 9 inches. If your filled backpack is larger, you'll need to check it.
